Nollywood actress, Victoria Inyama has tested positive for coronavirus (COVID-19) The actress, who presently resides in the UK, disclosed this on her Instagram page. According to her, she has been down with the virus for three weeks and is still hospitalized. Inyama posted a video from her
hospital bed showing her receiving treatment. Her post read: ”Gratitude, thank you @borisjohnsonuk and @mayorofldn for the lockdown. l could not have been more careful with the kids going to school etc.” She expressed gratitude that she was the one infected with the virus and not her children. “What a Christmas and New Year…what a 2021. Covid is a terrible virus ….l cannot even explain, so exhausting, three weeks and still counting,” her post added. 